    "text_verified": {
      "type": "Text",
      "props": {
        "text": "PR #47, +1,194/−21: New `POST /api/simulation/<id>/outcome` writes `outcome.json` to sim dir; gallery cards surface 📍/⚠/◑ outcome pills + coloured edge accents; new `/verified` route filters Explore to runs with recorded outcomes. `_read_outcome_file` strips non-http URLs as defense-in-depth so a corrupt artifact can't land `javascript:` on a card. EmbedDialog gains \"Mark outcome\" panel. Pivot from Apr 26 idea #1 — turns Bankr Terminal v2 Aave-sim citation (15M-view quote-tweet) into a permanent product surface.",
        "variant": "body"
      }
