        "text": "PR #48/#49, +540/−1: `require_admin_token` decorator on `/publish`, `/resolve`, `/outcome` — `Authorization: Bearer $MIROSHARK_ADMIN_TOKEN` with constant-time `hmac.compare_digest`. Fail-closed: 503 if env unset (so a misconfigured deploy doesn't silently ship an open mutation surface), 401 generic if wrong/missing (so probes can't fingerprint). 17 new unit tests.",
